snippet.title: Dolmenjord - Viking Islands - Trailer
snippet.description:
Arrange the Viking villages in the islands to expand their domains. After many years of battles, a group of Vikings decided it was time to conquer new lands. With the protection of the god Njord, a new clan specialized in navigation sets off in search of glory!

Creative and Art Direction - Allan Postal
Developed by Mens Sana Interactive

Coming soon on Steam. Add to your wishlist!
Dolmenjord - Viking Islands on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1899950/Dolmenjord__Viking_Islands/

Trailer edition - Allan Postal
